The '''Six Days of Rotterdam''' is a [[Six-day racing|six-day track cycling race]] held annually in [[Rotterdam]], the [[Netherlands]]. The event was first held in 1936.<ref>http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.eu/piste_6jours/6j_rotterdam.php</ref>

